 Us</a>\n<ul class="sub-menu">\n\t<li id="menu-item-75731" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-75731"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/about/our-mission/">Our Mission</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-75730" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-75730"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/our-funding/">Our Funding</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-75728" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-75728"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/our-staff/">Our Staff</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-103776" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-103776"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/undergraduate-fellows/">Undergraduate Fellows</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-76678" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-76678"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/awards/">Awards</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-75729" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-75729"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/about/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li id="menu-item-75130" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-75130"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/search/">Search</a></li>\n<li id="menu-item-75125" class="menu-item menu-item-type-custom menu-item-object-custom menu-item-has-children menu-item-75125"><a href="#">More</a>\n<ul class="sub-menu">\n\t<li id="menu-item-75126" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-75126"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/on-the-air/">FactCheck On the Air</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-75127" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-75127"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/party-lines/">Party Lines</a></li>\n\t<li id="menu-item-46908" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category menu-item-46908"><a href="http://www.factcheck.org/factcheck-mail